Football Jersey Kit iOS - Privacy Policy
Last Updated: January 24 2025
Introduction
The
Football Jersey Kit
app for iOS respects your privacy and is committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy outlines the data we collect, how we use it, and how we ensure its security.
Data We Do NOT Collect:
We do
not
collect any form of
analytical data
, including anonymous analytics or crash logs.
We do
not
access or read your
screenshots
or the data inside them. Text recognition, if used, is powered by Apple's
Vision Kit
and all processing occurs
on-device
. No data is sent to external servers.
The app requires an
Internet connection
only for features such as
auto-updates
. No other online activity is necessary for the app's basic functionality.
Permissions We Request:
Accessibility Permission
Required to take screenshots for use within the app. We do not read or store any data in your screenshots.
Device Information
When you activate a
license key
, we collect the following information to help manage your license:
Device Name
(e.g., “iPhone 14 Pro Max”) – Used for identifying your device in the
License Manager
.
Device ID (hardware identifier)
– Used to prevent misuse of the license key across unauthorized devices.
Data We Collect:
License Activation Data
Device Name
Device ID (hardware identifier)
We do
not
share this information with any third-party services.
Subscription Information:
The
Football Jersey Kit
offers the following subscription options:
Kit Monthly Subscription
Price: $3.99 per month
Auto-renews monthly.
Kit Yearly Subscription
Price: $14.99 per year
Auto-renews annually.
Important Subscription Terms:
Auto-Renewal:
By subscribing, you agree to the auto-renewal terms. This means that at the end of each billing period, your subscription will automatically renew and charge your account.
Managing Subscriptions:
You can manage or cancel your subscription at any time through your device's
Settings
>
Subscriptions
.
Third-Party Services:
We
do not
share any of your personal data with third-party services unless required by law.
Data Retention:
We will only retain the data we collect for as long as necessary to provide the services you request. We take commercially reasonable measures to protect your information from loss, theft, or unauthorized access.
External Links:
Our app may contain links to external websites. We are not responsible for the content or privacy practices of these third-party sites.
Your Rights:
You can choose to refuse our request for your personal information. However, doing so may limit your access to some features of the app.
Apple’s Standard EULA:
We use
Apple's standard End-User License Agreement (EULA)
for the app. You can view the EULA details here:
Apple Standard EULA
.
Changes to This Policy:
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page with an updated "Last Updated" date.
Contact Us:
If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy or how we handle your data, please feel free to contact us at:
Email:
thuyenpham.dev@gmail.com
Website:
https://futfc.vercel.app/
